{"tid":1987803,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"你知唔知你哋衰咩，就係衰在太認真","createTime":"2020-04-24T17:23:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T06:42:49.000Z","uid":79589,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fdc59544bde27c21e850359a2693a56b74f6961e","tid":1987803,"uid":79589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T17:23:49.000Z","msg":"點解黃圈互屌、屌泛民、屌熱狗雲黨永遠最落力，最熱烈？<br />\n<br />\n就係因為你哋太認真，認真到不斷反思、討厭、逐點反駁<br />\n<br />\n泛民係咁、連登仔又係咁<br />\n<br />\n變相就永遠係到就住一個點、一個問題係到拗，然後比對方不斷重複佢哋個論點係到洗人腦<br />\n<br />\n就好似何妖話林卓廷帶人入元朗一句，所有人就長篇大論去反駁、搵証據<br />\n但何妖由頭到尾都只會不斷重複林卓廷帶人入元朗<br />\n呢句野就好易令人入腦<br />\n<br />\n白兵、雲黨之類都係用咁樣方法去轉移視線<br />\n講一樣on9嘅嘢令你哋集中時間心思去反駁<br />\n<br />\n對付呢種人，麥美娟就示範比你哋睇點做: 離場<br />\n<br />\n因為根本唔值得哂時間哂心機去同佢哋理性討論，佢哋只會不斷spin 重複自己個論點去洗人腦<br />\n<br />\nDon&rsquo;t make stupid people famous <br />\n但呢句野講就醒，做就唔醒"},{"pid":"975940b6e15d81f8166bbffba59dd55f01b1eb50","tid":1987803,"uid":143451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T17:47:46.000Z","msg":"係囉 點會同無恥嘅人講證據道理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0abe562ab96ba4c6a0c7d578d69ad19e1659109d","tid":1987803,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T18:06:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a2edfe1ca7d15a2b1be39bd67b8f87b5bf0ef45","tid":1987803,"uid":223468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T18:11:31.000Z","msg":"正如唔好同五毛嘈交咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d9b9e5e32ece4055ac73bd4a8fc2b361cae5d7","tid":1987803,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a2edfe1ca7d15a2b1be39bd67b8f87b5bf0ef45","tid":1987803,"uid":223468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T18:11:31.000Z","msg":"正如唔好同五毛嘈交咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T18:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb4c50128e384fe815ebbe679ddf9ebe7e39a91f","tid":1987803,"uid":267964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T18:19:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"133026e6390bf97c3589752511e134921197755e","tid":1987803,"uid":79589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"975940b6e15d81f8166bbffba59dd55f01b1eb50","tid":1987803,"uid":143451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T17:47:46.000Z","msg":"係囉 點會同無恥嘅人講證據道理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T02:20:18.000Z","msg":"對付無賴就只能更無賴<br />\n之前杜民澤對呀叻又係一個示範<br />\n<br />\n藍絲之間充滿住呀叻之流，成日講我唔知、我唔識、我淨係知點點點<br />\n<br />\n你同無賴係到玩辯論，咪即係對牛彈琴？<br />\n<br />\n你比佢消耗更多時間同精力之餘，間接幫緊佢免費宣傳<br />\n<br />\n賭場唔怕你贏，只怕你唔入去<br />\n無賴唔怕你笑佢屌佢，只怕你唔應佢<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母仲係到講條白兵，咪就係免費幫佢推銷囉。<br />\n周圍d人本身唔知佢乜水，見你哋咁熱衷講就會好奇走去搵佢，推高佢個曝光率，宣傳埋佢啲論點<br />\n<br />\n2個月前有幾多人識條傻西？"},{"pid":"b0e7265bd67cc4b06da722767b686e5716a1374e","tid":1987803,"uid":79589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a2edfe1ca7d15a2b1be39bd67b8f87b5bf0ef45","tid":1987803,"uid":223468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T18:11:31.000Z","msg":"正如唔好同五毛嘈交咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T02:21:36.000Z","msg":"咪撚就係<br />\n五毛一句就釣到幾百個回覆，令佢個論點傳得更開"},{"pid":"34a050dd7fee69fcb811016a554ecf7734ab72f8","tid":1987803,"uid":15125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:42:49.000Z","msg":"上連登勿認真就基本野嚟<br />\n不過今年好多人上連登當大台咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}